Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去問問他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃乖乖的在這裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.58,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1\blur3}翻譯 十八 洛艾妖 校譯 洛艾妖 時間 倉鼠 後期 風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 坐下吧 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那個10th「月島獵人」不知道被什麼人射殺的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人舉報說 在附近目擊到你和我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目擊？這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 那這個就是偽報了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的嫌疑消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(334,283)\c&H879588&\3c&HEFF4ED&\fad(50,50)\shad0}「天野雪輝」 調查情況無……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不早就知道了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這也是有苦衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說的話就是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝 玩個遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「俄羅斯輪盤」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\c&H879588&\3c&HEFF4ED&\fad(50,50)\pos(572,211)\shad0}小雪和4th一起笑了呢。太好了。嫌疑解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs22\c&H879588&\3c&HEFF4ED&\fad(50,50)\pos(485,378)}小雪從調查室中走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4th是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕什麼 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是未來日記的持有者不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過和你的「無差別日記」不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的「搜查日記」 如果沒有事件發生的話 就沒有什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果在這裡殺死你的話 就成為事件了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我這麼做的話會被捕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我殺不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不是個壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 雪輝 終於輪到最後一發了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾啊 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們不是同盟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同盟解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的目標是成為神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你冷靜一點 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 恢復為正常的由乃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在你身邊了 所以不要緊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的槍聲是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後面的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們回家吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去叫救護車！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長 有沒有意識？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 救護隊還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行一般會上來第一槍直接瞄準頭部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話防彈衣不是沒意義了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過耳朵被打飛了真是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追！阻止他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君 你們知道自己在做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想做這種事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 再不停下的話我要開槍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去追嫌疑人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！不停的話我要開槍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄抵抗 把槍扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君 住手 這只是威懾射擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\3c&HEAF1E3&\c&H5A6F4D&\pos(481,178)\frz18.946\shad0}天野雪輝和我妻由乃兩人被帶來警署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs22\3c&HEAF1E3&\c&H5A6F4D&\pos(482,216)\frz17.935}嫌疑人「我妻由乃」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\shad0\3c&HEAF1E3&\c&H5A6F4D&\frz20.102\pos(581,219)}14歲 中年二年級學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\shad0\3c&HEAF1E3&\c&H5A6F4D&\frz18.827\pos(560,328)}櫻見警署內走廊內用鈍器擊打刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\shad0\3c&HEAF1E3&\c&H5A6F4D&\frz18.305\pos(573,344)}射擊同署內正在調查取證的刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\shad0\3c&HEAF1E3&\c&H5A6F4D&\frz20.061\pos(614,387)}罪名：故意傷人及殺人未遂罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\shad0\3c&HEAF1E3&\c&H5A6F4D&\frz20.102\pos(629,412)}警察們正全力追捕中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好啊 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全員！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能讓「天野雪輝」和「我妻由乃」兩人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力追捕兩位嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如遇抵抗 允許開槍！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(被4th襲擊2nd被擊斃了 dead end)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(「大恆商店」 被4th襲擊的我被射殺了 dead end)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被射殺了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,障礙就是 他們不是壞人這一事實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我煽動他們犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓雪輝陷入危險的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻一定會暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都按我所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們變成了警察所追捕的真正的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在我的計劃之內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 雪輝君！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我們兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據櫻見市警署的公佈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚一名少年和少女在警察詢問中搶走手槍並逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在市內全區域都拉起了非常警戒線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行嚴密的搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是目前為止尚未發現嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得忍住啊 外面很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據未來日記的預知 我們明天就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去買食物的商店前面跟警察展開了槍擊戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是反過來說的話 只要我們呆在這裡的話就是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是肚子餓了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我方便下啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…… 不要聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不能就一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不方便的地方也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 爸爸經常給我買甜甜圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸和媽媽為什麼離婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們大人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要背叛我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很臭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 是甜甜圈的味道啦 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來須警官的夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來探望誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H657D73&\3c&HE1E9E6&\shad0\fs22\org(509,142)\frx2\fry0\frz0.901\pos(519,62)}小雪幫我治療手臂了哦。謝謝你，小雪。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H657D73&\3c&HE1E9E6&\shad0\fs22\org(509,142)\frx2\fry0\frz0.901\pos(546,180)}小雪看見我尿尿了，好丟臉……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H657D73&\3c&HE1E9E6&\shad0\fs20\org(509,142)\frx2\fry0\frz0.901\pos(617,292)}小雪跟蹤4th的女人。也許是個反擊的好機會。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HE1E9E6&\shad0\fs22\org(509,142)\frx2\fry0\frz0.901\pos(579,399)\c&H6D5A60&}小雪去廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命真夠硬啊 還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了啊 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9th
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是來對地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好無聊著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你就給我好好聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想被破壞難得的約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…這個… 你都做了些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻冒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個 快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干毛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻見醫院又發生爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好的人手立即出發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好死不死的雪輝他們居然出現在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先過去的話 你那姘頭肯定會把橋拿掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放手的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先過去的話才不知道你會幹些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不會做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 由乃還有槍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵架啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 1st 現在我們先結成同盟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我還會告訴你為什麼4th會背叛你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來須
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經從日記上瞭解到你那邊的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就過去 你再撐一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然要背叛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再被捲入你們大人的這些爛事情裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 我現在是站在你這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9th 你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道想背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 你果然是要背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你先聽人說話好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不論何時都是在站小雪這邊的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了啊 大家都把我當小鬼來耍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會背叛你哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我解釋下現狀 9th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒辦法相信了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都把我當猴耍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有5分鐘就到了 你們沒辦法逃脫這個包圍網的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有把你當猴耍啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是由乃你說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背叛我的話 我連你一起殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘管你啊！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爽多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(420,401)\c&H84998B&\3c&HEEF1EF&\shad0}無路可逃。9th雨流美彌音被4th襲擊。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 4th就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法從這個醫院逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要拿張王牌在手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了要跟你說4th襲擊你的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有一個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在遊戲中我出局的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你們是前陣子的……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎啊 小小新婚夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須曜 4th的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來須警官的……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月被診斷腦部患病 還有3個月的命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是為了救兒子 才想要當神的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了聽他的要求 跟他聯手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在也解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要聯手打倒4th
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人就是王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 你們肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個與其讓個半死不活的小鬼吃 還不如給我們吃更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經踏入大人的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經無法再當個小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人得自己餵飽自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與4th的籠中之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃的話 死的會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下決心要保護由乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要做這種事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豎起DEAD END旗幟的三人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有夠遜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們暫且算是同盟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是要打倒4th的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新未來同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:01.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}ココロが死ぬよ　自分のためないが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:01.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}心已不隨己地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:03.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}引き金になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:03.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}做拋磚引玉之用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:12.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}助かる君えと　信じて君からもれだ声に呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:12.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}被我所信任的 拯救我的你之聲所呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:18.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}奇跡を　いもの追っか駆ける悲劇は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:18.25,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}那奇跡 那追逐虛像而去的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:20.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}終わらないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:20.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}永無終止之日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:29.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}闇の奥で繰り返す叫び いとに痛み悪意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:29.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}在黑暗泥沼中不斷的吶喊 及那深沉的惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:32.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}選ばれしだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:32.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}這就是被選中的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:36.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}泣きたくない　これ以上愛たくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:36.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}不願再哭泣 再不願去愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}燃える　愛しいさが通差した
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:40.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}燃燒的愛意卻穿體而過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}愛きて　泣きたく追い駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}抹掉淚水 去追逐那愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:48.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}誰にも　止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:48.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}誰都無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:53.55,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}これは未来　それとも夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:53.55,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}此乃未來 抑或是夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}答えは何処だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:56.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}答案不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:01.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}これが今を　試す扉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:01.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}若此為如今的試煉之門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}壊すは開けれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}毀滅也無法將其開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:08.04,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}どしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:08.04,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}該如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:14.82,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEC00C1&\pos(566,28)}姆魯姆魯{\c&H5B6F5D&}老師的{\c&HFBF9F9&}秘密未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:14.82,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz359.479\fs32\c&H29CEF6&\u1\pos(424,133)}姆魯姆魯刑警的出動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:14.82,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H073027&\fs35\move(466,381,451,378)\c&HFDFAFC&}西島真澄篇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 課長 您在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在幹什麼啊 會議就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到這個時候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨流美彌音的調查進行得還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 沒什麼大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長 你的氛圍感覺好像不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 不論怎麼看我都是來須圭悟好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如髮型什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是疲勞過度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要打起精神來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是犯罪現場的話 你早就讓犯人給逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白就好 你請我吃豬肉蓋澆飯就原諒你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是貨真價實的豬肉蓋澆飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟平時的一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察果然是要在審訊室吃著豬肉蓋澆飯 然後審訊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島 快給我從實招了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經掌握事實了 早招早輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣啦 這時候你應該……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不上道啊 電視劇裡不是常演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為什麼當警察的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 警察先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一不小心……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去好好贖罪吧 你肯定可以重新做人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…… 真的是… 對不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(237,0)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島 去吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬肉蓋澆飯是吧 我剛剛已經端去審訊室了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您請先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做完這個馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務區外
